metadata.name: Mount Pepo
metadata.description:
Mount Pepo is the tallest and juiciest mountain in the whole Watermelon Country. 

It symbolises the Watermelon Land's power as a particular undivided unitary country held together by sugar-drenched extreme force - white and pointy at the top, ripe and fetid at the bottom.

---

I am a prolific artist using AI and digital art methods in conjunction to create new art - underlining "new art". This technology gives all artists the speed and confidence to push their limits, and I, for one, intend to!

4267px X 4267px
